{"tid":998569,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"信用卡積分黨召喚+睇人仆街最開心","createTime":"2019-01-28T05:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T17:38:10.000Z","uid":156791,"like":44,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"294c7dc9e150732bfce20cb1d581d0557dd742fd","tid":998569,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:23:28.000Z","msg":"有玩開信用卡都知人妖小屍的惡行。為支持政府打擊逃稅，漏報稅行為，  請各位巴絲出一分力 email 去稅局 。  taxinfo@ird.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n身邊有朋友仲睇緊呢班 KOL 的，都勸佢地唔好再用垃圾 mgm link 申請卡 thanks.<br />\n<br />\nTemplate 係下面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n致 稅務局調查專員:<br />\n<br />\n本人有關&quot;網上紅人KOL&quot;所收之饋贈應否納入稅務款項有所不清楚，現時有很多知名KOL,例如「張鎌安」網名「小斯」以信用卡members get members簡稱&rdquo;MGM&rdquo;之好友推薦計劃連結供讀者及fans申請信用卡或訂購酒店機票，從指定網絡連結中獲取大量銀行積分及現金作佣金收入，由於相關積分和現金回贈金額巨大，舉例， 「張鎌安」現時主推一張由發卡機構American express (美國運通)之美國運通白金卡。<br />\n<br />\n而該卡的MGM計劃，每成功推薦一個新客戶成功申請，推薦人可以收到250,000的信用卡積分。250,000的AE信用卡積分可以換取到 而AE的積分可以透過Pay with Points計劃每300轉成1$港幣，而250,000可換取現金833元。參考計劃鏈結如下。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.americanexpress.com/hk/ch/campaigns/paywithpoints/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americanexpress.com%2Fhk%2Fch%2Fcampaigns%2Fpaywithpoints%2Findex.html&d=8FWVfFAHAUFKZ2pbkJ9dxeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=90ef1bf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.americanexpress.com/hk/ch/campaigns/paywithpoints/index.html</a><br />\n(由於各銀行之推薦計劃太多上述只作其中一個參考)<br />\n<br />\n如果以 自僱人士身份，接收信用卡積分作饋贈，而該饋贈金額更可能成為主要收入來源。請問是否需要納入稅務款項，如不是的話，如果我以自僱身份接收虛擬貨幣作報酬，請問是否需要需要納入稅務款項。<br />\n<br />\n張氏收入範圍更涉及媒體訪問、各銀行訪問、媒體雜誌犒件、出席各項公關活動 及 其網站上的GOOGLE  ADsense每月保守估計逾20萬港元，盼請貴局能夠徹底調查該人士的相關收入有否如實申報予稅局，祈得到明確答確。<br />\n<br />\n現附上張鎌安生意連結以便蒐證<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FlyForMiles/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFlyForMiles%2F&d=8FWVfFAHAUFKZ2pbkJ9dxeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=68d1612e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FlyForMiles/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://flyformiles.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fflyformiles.hk%2F&d=8FWVfFAHAUFKZ2pbkJ9dxeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=a6e7e3c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://flyformiles.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n銀行或信用卡機構名單：美國通運銀行、香港渣打銀行、星展銀行、東亞銀行、香港花旗銀行等等<br />\n<br />\n公關活動及電視真人節目名單：ViuTV、TVB、領展等等<br />\n<br />\n祝 工作順利"},{"pid":"45e9002d73db3e9001387cb6a195cfd74eec053a","tid":998569,"uid":101714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ebc3471d21b224c0cf58f2e137653fdca6b337","tid":998569,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T09:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3175cb827a25f70e57cdb991123edcd948914af0","tid":998569,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T09:20:58.000Z","msg":"1823 都work<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771cd0bbb1369e8190094dd604d34bc5eb072444","tid":998569,"uid":96008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T09:29:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4b84fa38b88686b80d9860392aa0292585328f81","tid":998569,"uid":132488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T09:30:21.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"c6bda82a725cee5f4e5c041a23bf532b210c2e15","tid":998569,"uid":132595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T09:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f19b960d904b116a5e3879ddc1d902b5c7146d0","tid":998569,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8ff5c78749a75ad6615b28fb37dc033ab34abc","tid":998569,"uid":153609,"lik